<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١ - وَذِي غِرَّةٍ أَنْذَرْتُهُ مِنْ أَمَامِهِ ... فَلَمَّا عَصَانِي فِي الْمَضَاءِ تَقَدَّمَا<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٩٣٠)</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ الْقُطَامِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الوافر)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١ - وَمَعْصِيَةِ الشَّفِيقِ عَلَيْكَ مِمَّا ... تَزِيدُكَ مَرَّةً مِنْهُ اسْتِمَاعَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٩٣١)</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ حُصَيْنُ بْنُ الْمُنْذِرِ الرَّقَاشِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>١ - أمَرْتُكَ أَمْراً حَازِماً فَعَصَيْتَنِي ... فَأَصْبَحْتَ مَسْلُوبَ الإِمَارَةِ نَادِمَا<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>٢ - فَمَا أَنَا بِالْبَاكِي عَلَيْكَ صَبَابَةً ... وَمَا أَنَا بِالدَّاعِي لِتَرْجِعَ سَالِمَا<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c2">(٩٣٢)</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ الْمُتَلَمِّسُ الضُّبَعِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>١ - عَصَانِي فَلَمْ يَلْقَ الرَّشَادَ وَإِنَّمَا ... تَبَيَّنُ مِنْ أَمْرِ الْغَوِيِّ عَوَاقِبُهْ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٢ - فَأَصْبَحَ مَحْمُولاً عَلَى ظَهْرِ أَلَّةٍ ... تَمُجُّ نَجِيعَ الْجَوْفِ مِنْهَا تَرَائِبُهْ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c2">(٩٣٣)</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ زُهيْرُ بْنُ كَلْحَبَةَ الْيَرْبُوعِيُّ:</span> <span class="c2">(الطويل)</span><a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>